{
  "stem": "11722.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] well, in the ghetto, they came around, and they said that before they take us away that everybody should give up their jewelry.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember my mother had diamond earrings, and she took them off and she gave them to them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Otherwise they would have probably been yanked off anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember the train stopped on the border someplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they opened up-- I think they gave us some water, and they said, anybody else has got jewelry, you better give it up because it's going to be confiscated and you'll have to pay a heavy penalty if they find it on you.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some people gave up some jewelry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] what I heard since then that military trains had the priority many times.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, these transports, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they derailed them to a side track, and they sometimes waited a week on the side track before they continued on to Birkenau, Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when they opened up these [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] cattle cars, half of the people were dead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyway, we arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember they started yelling, [GERMAN]!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Get out!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Leave all your belongings behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's going to follow you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Stand in line.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "All able-bodied men to the left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "All women and children [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And there was the people with striped garb.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We didn't know who they were or where we were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They kept saying [GERMAN]!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Go to work!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My father understood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I was 14 and a half years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He told me to stand tall and lie about my age, tell them I'm 18.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I had my brother, who was younger.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
